videoSnippet.title: Kasparov beats Journalist Leon Watson after Car Crash
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Leon Watson Twitter: Interviewed the great @Kasparov63 over a chess board today after his car crash. I can confirm his head still works... mine perhaps not

Leon Watson vs Garry Kasparov

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. e4 d6 5. Nf3 O-O 6. Be2 e5 7. O-O Nc6 8. d5 Ne7 9. b4 Nh5 10. Re1 a5 11. Ba3 b6 12. c5 axb4 13. Bxb4 bxc5
